<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">śubhamastu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tiṟipuvaṉacakkaṟavaṟutti koṉerimaikoṇṭāṉ naraiyaṉūrṉāṭṭu Uṭaiyapirāṭṭiccaruppetimaṅkalattu koḻiñcipāṭiyil Uṭaiyār Aḻakiyacokkaṉāṟkku teṉpoṅ<supplied reason="omitted">ka</supplied>lūṟkkāṉāṭṭu
<lb n="2"/>nimmaṇi nañcai puñcai ṉānkellaik kuḷppaṭṭavaiyum Aṇṭāvūrṉāṭṭu Amarapūṇṭi nañcai puñcai ṉānkellaik kuḷppaṭṭatum yinta Iraṇṭūrum Iṉṉayiṉār Aḻakiya cokkaṉāṟkku pūcai viniyokattukku kuṭuttom Itukku
<lb n="3"/>Akutam ceyitavaṉ <hi rend="grantha">gaṅ</hi> kaikkaraiyil kā<hi rend="grantha">rā</hi> mpacuvaik konṟa pāpatte pova<hi rend="grantha">n</hi> teyiva pirāmaṇaraikkoṉṟa pāpatte pova<hi rend="grantha">n</hi> yinta taṉmattai naṭattiṉavan Aṟupattuṉālu tiruviḷaiyāṭṭum tiruviḷaiyāṭiṉa Aḻakiyacokkaṉār
<lb n="4"/>Aruḷaippeṟṟu Añkaiykkaṇṇiyār Aruḷaippeṟṟu piṟutuvirācciyam paṇṇi cukame yiruppaṉ Itu virapāṇṭiyatevar Upaiyam <g ref="sym:tam-pillaiyarCuli" type="punctuation"> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> </g>
</p>

